<problem id="fs-id1280259">
<para id="fs-id1037597">An angle measures <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>25°</m:mtext><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Find its: <span class="token">ⓐ</span> supplement <span class="token">ⓑ</span> complement.</para></problem>
